snippet.title: New Super Mario 64 DS Trailer - NFGD 2022
snippet.description:
Watch the full presentation for NFGD here: https://youtu.be/dPRaePoZN50

New Super Mario 64 DS is a mod of SM64DS that adds over 10+ new and original custom levels, as well as custom Music, Sound Effects, and a new experience overall.

There are more previews and updates about this project on my channel, and more to come soon.

I don't have an exact release date, but I will try my best to release or finish this project sometime in 2023.

Lastly, huge thanks to the SM64DS hacking community for helping, too.
